		<div class="body" id="body">
				<p><span class="heading1">Welcome!</span> </p>
				<p><strong>Harmatan and Oakridge Leathers 2008 Ltd. manufacture  fine goatskin and calfskin bookbinding	leathers. </strong></p>
				<p>Our leathers are created using traditional methods at our small, highly specialised tannery at Higham Ferrers, Northamptonshire, UK - an area traditionally	associated with the production of leather and leather goods. From here our	quality leathers are	distributed worldwide to a diverse range of clients who enjoy working with these fine skins. </p>
				<p><strong>Please note that we do not sell any of our products via eBay.
								Please beware of cheaper but poorly or incorrectly
								tanned bookbinding leather	you may see advertised
								on	the internet.</strong></p>
		</div><!--body-->
